quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  17,94,"Ha…óaali yim…ďe …ďen nde …ďe gom…óinta tuma nde peewalngal arunoo …ďe, si wanaa fii …ďe wi'ii: \"E hara Alla nulay …ďanndinke Nulaa…óo"
  17,95,"Maaku: \"Si tawiino laatinoke ka leydi Malaa'ikaa…ďe hi…ďe yaha ko …ďe deewu…ďe, Men jippinayno e ma…ď…ďe immorde ka kammu Malaa'ikaajo Nulaa…óo"
  17,96,"Maaku: \"Alla yonii Seedii…óo hakkunde an e mon, pellet Kanko O wonii Humpitii…óo Reenu…óo jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen"
  17,97,"On mo Alla fewni ko on woni feewu…óo, …ďe O majjini …ďen a he…ďantaa…ďe walloo…ďe ko woori Mo. Men moo…ďay …ďe √Īalde darngal e dow geece ma…ď…ďe …óen ko …ďe wumu…ďe e mbobi…óu= fahdube …ďe e faa…óu…ďe, werde ma…ď…ďe nden ko jahannama tuma kala nge rocci Men …ďeydana …ďe hu…ď…ďunge"
  17,98,"∆äun ko njoddi ma…ď…ďe, sabu kam…ďe …ďe yeddii Aayeeje Amen …óen, …ďe wi'i: \"E hay si men wonii ∆īi'e e mbu…óu e hara menen ko men immintintee…ďe tagu hesu"
  17,99,"Enee, …ďee yi'aali, wonnde Alla On Tagu…óo kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin ko O Hattan…óo nde O tagata yeru ma…ď…ďe, O wa…óani …ďe lajal [caate] sikke alaa e maggal. Too√Īoo…ďe …ďen salii si wanaa yeddugol"
  17,100,"Maaku: \"Sinndo onon hi…óon marunoo ngaluuji Hinnayee Joomi an on, ontuma, on jogitotono kulol nafkugol, ne…ó…óanke on wonii nguddo"